{"title":"厦门抒情","authors":["董耀章"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":10,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"厦门抒情（外二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"董耀章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鹭江浓彩染，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧中见湛蓝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天在水中溶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纷呈画一卷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海鸥雪翼闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲤鱼喷花串，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轮机声沸沸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帆影点点远。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游子出海港，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情思剪不断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耿耿赤子心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与国常相伴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海鸥展翅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湿风掀波涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨点如鼓敲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海鸥掠水飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双翼健且矫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秉性爱弄潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不惧风雨啸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生死恋大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啼声逐浪高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台岛遥相望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离人珠泪抛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"切切思乡情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回归志不摇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓浪声声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓浪屿上行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹如入仙境，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿波托青山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岛映水晶宫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祥云头上飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长龙脚下腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曲径通幽处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗情郁葱葱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珍珠灿若星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珊瑚砌翠峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓浪声澎湃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"催我踏征程。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}